{"tid":1565391,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[搶救CCTV][請馬上行動] 831之謎 保存路面CCTV[商舖/車Cam] 至關緊要 證據黎架","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T13:26:04.000Z","uid":264983,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"02c39db9bbf21454d7d48deaa74f4c2e3badb16c","tid":1565391,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:31:01.000Z","msg":"831太子封站24小時, 班狗同狗官一直拖, <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但依刻有一樣野, 極之緊要但未宣傳夠, 唔可以再拖, 就係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫齊人保留當晚 CCTV 片段  [商舖/車Cam] </span></span><br />\n<br />\n一般 CCTV 最多保留2星期, 依家差唔多盡啦, <br />\n唔好屌話咁遲, 我都係突然心血來潮諗到.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔該唔該唔該</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">果幾個黨鐵站附近既商舖 (太子/旺角/油麻地/石硤尾/荔枝角),</span> <br />\n或者<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有可能泊過係街度既車,</span></strong><br />\n如果你個 View 係可能影到馬路既<br />\n快啲攞個 Cam 睇下先. <br />\n<br />\n<strong>近 醫院/狗屋/狗會 或 其他敏感地方既, 譬如啲殮房之類呀<br />\n而其他地方有機會影到馬路既, </strong><br />\n唔該都幫手<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">望一望下當晚 (831 2300開始至第二朝天光前) 段片啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">最緊要唔好遲左 CCTV 片段會被覆蓋左呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依家要做既係:</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1.想追查831既, 入 TG [還我831真相]</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MeFsV1amUJvxp-xUvnuIwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMeFsV1amUJvxp-xUvnuIwg&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=039959c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MeFsV1amUJvxp-xUvnuIwg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 組隊幫手去各區街舖叫街舖留 CCTV <br />\n(呢個一定要快!!!!!)<br />\n<br />\n3. Share 呢篇出去 Facebook / IG / WhatsApp<br />\n<br />\n4. 要求黨鐵保留埋石硤尾/油麻地/荔枝⻆站既CCTV</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>主要資料來源:</ins></strong><br />\n831 太子站死者有可能經石硤尾站 運送到警察遊樂會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1564900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1564900</a><br />\n<br />\n[重開大整合] 831事件未必得2個死(2) 荔枝角站石硤尾站cctv都好關鍵<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1546103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1546103</a><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港  時代革命"},{"pid":"0b622079aaa8593d7846d6fbae84831ae1815a2f","tid":1565391,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:31:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ec58cfbdf1c8a8768e49b595e1bff4c3698acab0","tid":1565391,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=82e447a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGhzabb2g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區集合地點!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n油麻地、佐敦、尖沙咀: 梳士巴利公園(太空館附近)<br />\n荃灣、大窩口、青衣: 荃灣公園(海濱長廊)、青衣海濱長廊<br />\n葵興、葵芳、荔景: 林士德遊樂場、葵涌運動場<br />\n美孚: 嶺南之風<br />\n太子、旺角: 花墟公園<br />\n荔枝角、長沙灣: 長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗: 通州街公園<br />\n油塘、藍田: 油塘道遊樂場<br />\n將軍澳、寶琳、坑口、康城<br />\n中西區（西區、中環、金鐘、半山、山頂）<br />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"485173a04dd9252e2753c25672e056efc31ba831","tid":1565391,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:32:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3beb016a7bf78cbabe0ee4dcd65beb7fc8c89437","tid":1565391,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:32:48.000Z","msg":"石硤尾站出面啲車cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e949e30309850d6bc817e8c305b64931e70c004","tid":1565391,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gZH76Gs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgZH76Gs.jpg&h=45845535&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NrSLTms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNrSL